\begin_layout Subsubsection
回归系数的置信区间
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\beta_{j}$
\end_inset

的估计值为
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\beta_{j}}$
\end_inset

，估计值的标准差为:
\begin_inset Formula $se(\hat{\beta_{j}}),i=1,2,\cdots,m$
\end_inset

，其中
\begin_inset Formula $c_{ii}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $C=(X^{T}X)^{-1}$
\end_inset

对角线上的第i个元素。因此估计值
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\beta_{j}}$
\end_inset

的置信度为1-
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

的置信区间为:
\begin_inset Formula $(\hat{\beta_{j}}-Z_{\frac{\alpha}{2}}sd,\hat{\beta_{j}}+Z_{\frac{\alpha}{2}}sd)$
\end_inset

，取
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

=0.05,可以求得如下表所示:
\end_layout

